Delivery Order Incoming!
===============================================

Customer's Info:
----------------
Name   : <%= @delivery.name %>
Email  : <%= @delivery.email %>
Phone  : <%= @delivery.phone %>
WeChat : <%= @delivery.wechat %>

Listed Items to be Delivered:
-----------------------------

<% if @delivery.products.count > 0 %>
  <% @delivery.products.each do |product| %>
    <%= product.name %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

Other Items to be Delivered:
-----------------------------

<% if @delivery.delivery_items.count > 0 %>
  <% @delivery.delivery_items.each do |item| %>
    <%= item.name %> | <%= item.address %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

Destination:
------------
<%= @delivery.address.full_address %>
<%= @delivery.address.apartment %>
<%= @delivery.address.city + ", " + @delivery.address.state + ", " + @delivery.address.postal_code %>
